ActCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
PrecisAppointment of ROBERT SANDERSON of Vancouver West, British Columbia, to be Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year, or until such time as a new Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first.
